These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
House: cape-cod, tower, ranch-style, cottage
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, chess, skydiving, writing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, old-henry, game, baccarat
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, september, december, january
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, horse, mouse
 1. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the tower house##1
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is the cape-cod house##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 8. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 9. the game-smoker is the cape-cod house##1
10. the owner of the horse is the old-henry-smoker##1
11. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| House          | tower    | ranch-style      | cape-cod  | cottage     |
| Hobby         | writing    | skydiving   | card-games | chess      |
| Cigar   | old-henry       | bongani | game     | baccarat    |
| Birthday   | january | september         | august  | december    |
| Pet           | horse      | mouse       | chinchilla | guinea-pig |

