.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, french, japanese, italian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, satire, spy
City: liverpool, miami, edinburgh, rome
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, photographer, entrepreneur, videographer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, handball, parkour, skiing
 1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the videographer##1
 4. the italian is on the far right##1
 5. the chinese is on the right of the french##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the japanese##1
 7. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 8. the photographer is the person traveling to rome##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
10. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far right##1
11. the japanese is on the left of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Nationality      | french      | chinese     | japanese    | italian |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | drama   | satire   | spy           |
| City   | miami  | rome     | edinburgh    | liverpool         |
| Job           | videographer         | photographer | entrepreneur     | mechanic        |
| Sport         | cricket     | skiing  | handball | parkour       |

