4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, mouse, rabbit
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, iris, zinnia, tulip
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, comedy, western, fantasy
 1. the person who growsbellflower is on the far left##1
 2. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 3. the coach is the owner of the rabbit##1
 4. the pilot is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 5. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the engineer##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is the coach##1
 7. the chinese is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 9. the french is the owner of the frog##1
10. the british is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
11. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
12. the coach is on the right of the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Job          | security-guard    | engineer      | coach  | pilot   |
| Nationality   | french     | chinese      | british | american      |
| Pet           | frog       | fish         | rabbit  | mouse         |
