.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, soy-milk, sprite
There 4 different types of food: garlic, grapefruit, pepper, raspberry
4 different games are played: billiard, domino, backgammon, snooker
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, drawing, photography, traveling
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, dancer, fisherman, scientist
 1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the dancer##1
 3. the dancer is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
 5. the doctor is on the far left##1
 6. the fisherman is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 9. the person playing domino is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
12. the scientist is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | sprite   | cola      | coffee     |
| Food          | pepper     | garlic   | raspberry | grapefruit |
| Game   | domino | backgammon | billiard   | snooker       |
| Hobby           | drawing       | filmmaking      | traveling     | photography |
| Job     | doctor    | fisherman     | scientist     | dancer     |

