4 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, lizard, snake
 1. the person traveling to prague is the owner of the snake##1
 2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left##1
 3. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is the person playing scrabble##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 6. the person traveling to london is on the far right##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 8. the owner of the snake is the person traveling to prague##1
 9. the person playing whist is the owner of the lizard##1
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
11. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
12. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
14. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |    4     |
