There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, coffee, mirinda
4 different games are played: whist, chess, bridge, backgammon
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, ship, van
 1. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person playing backgammon##1
 4. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 5. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 7. the person driving the ship is the person playing backgammon##1
 8. the person playing whist is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
10. the person playing bridge is the person driving the van##1
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is the old-henry-smoker##1
12. the person drinking coffee is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Hobby         | dancing   | gardening | skydiving    | card-games  |
| Cigar   | cain    | old-henry | dunhill      | blend |
