10. the person eating asparagus is the person playing monopoly##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
12. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Food    | pineapple     | corn  | asparagus       | artichoke      |
| Hobby       | singing    | writing        | collecting  | drawing      |
| Nationality         | nigerian  | argentine | british | egyptian |
| Game         | billiard | backgammon          | monopoly         | whist      |
| Transport   | subway     | helicopter     | trike       | van          |

