.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, september, january, august
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, magic-tricks, video-games, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller, western
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, climbing, surfing, golf
4 different games are played: whist, bridge, domino, snooker
 1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in september is the person watching western movies##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 4. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 9. the person playing bridge is the person watching thriller movies##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
11. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Birthday      | august       | january      | september      | march    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | video-games | magic-tricks | dancing  |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller    | mystery     | western      | disaster |
| Sport   | surfing  | golf     | lacrosse    | climbing  |
| Game           | bridge  | snooker       | whist          | domino      |

