.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, plum, raspberry, tomato
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, rock-climbing, singing, video-games
House: palace, wooden, cape-cod, gothic-revival
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, coach, musician, videographer
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, polish, pakistani, thai
 1. the musician is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 3. the pakistani is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 4. the cape-cod house is on the right of the palace house##1
 5. the palace house is on the left of the thai##1
 6. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the turkish##1
 7. the thai is on the left of the person eating lime##1
 8. the videographer is on the right of the person eating lime##1
 9. the wooden house is on the right of the person eating plum##1
10. the videographer is the person eating raspberry##1
11. the chef is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
13. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |      3      |       4       |
| Food          | tomato      | plum     | lime        | raspberry     |
| Hobby         | singing     | chess    | video-games | rock-climbing |
| House   | palace | cape-cod  | wooden      | gothic-revival       |
| Job         | musician      | chef | coach     | videographer        |
| Nationality     | pakistani   | thai     | turkish  | polish       |

