.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, spy, family, horror
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, vegafina, ritmeester, dannemann
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, entrepreneur, security-guard, social-worker
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, 7up, soy-milk, cola
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter, ship, snowmobile
 1. the social-worker is the cain-smoker##1
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 3. the social-worker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 4. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the doctor##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is the dannemann-smoker##1
 6. the person watching family movies is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
 8. the doctor is the person driving the motorbike##1
 9. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the person watching horror movies is the person drinking cola##1
11. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
12. the person drinking cola is on the left of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Movie-Genre        | spy    | horror        | martial-arts        | family      |
| Cigar       | ritmeester       | cain       | vegafina      | dannemann |
| Job         | entrepreneur | social-worker | security-guard | doctor      |
| Beverage         | lemonade          | cola         | 7up           | soy-milk    |
| Transport   | ship         | scooter       | snowmobile     | motorbike   |

 